This article is a '''comparison of [[issue tracking system]]s''' that are notable, including [[bug tracking system]]s, [[help desk]] and [[Service Desk (ITSM)|service desk]] issue tracking systems, as well as [[IT asset management|asset management]] systems. The comparison includes client-server application, distributed and hosted systems.

